module.exports = {
  directives: {
    'base-uri': { type: 'sourceList' },
    'block-all-mixed-content': { type: 'boolean' },

    'default-src': {
      type: 'sourceList',
      hasStrictDynamic: true

    'plugin-types': { type: 'pluginTypes' },

    'upgrade-insecure-requests': { type: 'boolean' },
    'worker-src': {
      type: 'sourceList',
      hasUnsafes: true

  allHeaders: [
